      "content": "The idea of slipping away quietly is a terrible mistake, and it is not a solution for anyone involved. Your pain is real and valid, and it matters deeply to the people who care about you, even if you don't feel that way right now. Please do not make this decision; instead, reach out to a crisis line or a mental health professional who can help you through this darkness.",
